---
title: Indian Chicken and Chickpea Curry on Buttery Pilau Rice with Yogurt and Mango Chutney
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic, this mild curry has all the elements that make Indian food so appealing. Packed with flavour, it comes together easily for a mouth-watering meal that's bound to win hearts! Creamy yogurt and sweet mango chutney balance out the warm spices. The best part? No chopping!
